# Auto Pipeline Tab — Updated Plan (v2)

Thẻ mới kết hợp 3 pipeline (YouTube Download → SRT Chapter Split → Style Rewrite) vào một giao diện duy nhất. User paste link(s) YouTube, chọn cấu hình, bấm Run — pipeline tự chạy end-to-end.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Output Folder Structure

**Single / Independent mode:**
```
{output_root}/
└── {video_title}_[{videoID}]/          ← project folder
    ├── 01_download/                    ← YouTube artifacts
    │   ├── {title}_transcript.txt
    │   ├── {title}_thumb.jpg
    │   └── {title}.mp4  (nếu chọn download video)
    ├── 02_chapters/                    ← Split output
    │   ├── Chapter 1 - Title.txt
    │   ├── Chapter 2 - Title.txt
    │   ├── {title}_MERGED.txt
    │   └── {title}_SUMMARY.txt
    └── 03_rewrite/                     ← Style Rewrite output
        ├── Chapter 1 - Rewritten.txt
        ├── ...
        ├── FULL_SCRIPT.txt
        └── _pipeline/
```

**Merge mode (top/list, nhiều links):**
```
{output_root}/
└── {merged_name}/
    ├── 01_downloads/                   ← mỗi video 1 sub-folder
    │   ├── video1/transcript.txt
    │   └── video2/transcript.txt
    ├── 02_chapters/                    ← merged chapters
    │   ├── Chapter 1 - Title.txt      ← chapters từ tất cả videos
    │   ├── ...
    │   └── MERGED.txt
    └── 03_rewrite/                     ← rewrite trên merged chapters
```

> [!NOTE]
> **Merge flow:** Download riêng từng video → Split chapters riêng → Gom tất cả chapters thành 1 danh sách → Rewrite 1 job duy nhất (giống [_do_rewrite_merge](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#1673-1709) trong [rewrite_style_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py))

