### Pipeline Flow — Chi tiết

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start["User paste URLs & Run"] --> Count{"URLs count?"}
    Count -->|1| Single["→ Single mode"]
    Count -->|>1| Ask{"Popup: 'Independent' or 'Merge'?<br/>(Merge chỉ cho Top/List)"}
    Ask -->|Independent| EachURL["Loop từng URL"]
    Ask -->|Merge| MergeMode["Merge mode"]
    
    %% ═══ STEP 1: Download ═══
    EachURL --> DL["Step 1: Download"]
    Single --> DL
    MergeMode --> MDL["Step 1: Download tất cả videos"]
    
    DL --> DL1["get_video_info()"]
    DL1 --> DL2["get_transcript_ytdlp() → fallback API"]
    DL2 --> DL3["extract_timestamps()"]
    DL3 --> DL4["build_transcript_file()"]
    DL4 --> DL5["(optional) download_video + thumbnail"]
    DL5 --> Classify["AI classify_script_type()"]
    
    MDL --> DL1
    
    %% ═══ CLASSIFY CHECK ═══
    Classify --> MMatch{"AI type == user type?"}
    MMatch -->|yes| Split["Step 2: Split"]
    MMatch -->|no| Popup["⚠ Popup: 'Video ABC detected as Narrative<br/>but mode is Top/List. Continue?'"]
    Popup -->|continue| Split
    Popup -->|cancel| Stop["Stop"]
    
    %% ═══ STEP 2: Split ═══
    Split --> S1["split_chapters()"]
    S1 --> S2["verify_chapters()"]
    S2 --> S3["punctuate_chapters() (if SRT)"]
    S3 --> S4["save_chapters()"]
    S4 --> MergeCheck{"Merge mode?"}
    MergeCheck -->|no| Rewrite["Step 3: Rewrite"]
    MergeCheck -->|yes| Collect["Gom chapters từ tất cả videos"]
    Collect --> Rewrite
    
    %% ═══ STEP 3: Rewrite ═══
    Rewrite --> R1{"mode?"}
    R1 -->|Top/List| R2["Top/List Review pipeline<br/>(giống _do_renew_review)"]
    R1 -->|Narrative| R3["Narrative pipeline<br/>(giống _do_renew_style)"]
    R2 --> Done["✅ Done + Excel update"]
    R3 --> Done
```

### Key Behaviors

1. **AI Classify + Mismatch popup**: Sau khi download transcript, gọi [classify_script_type()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#150-187). Nếu kết quả khác mode user chọn → popup hiện **tiêu đề video** cụ thể + giải thích:
   ```
   ⚠ Video không khớp format:
   • "Top 10 Best Handguns 2024" — AI detect: Top/List (bạn chọn: Narrative)
   
   [Tiếp tục với mode gốc]  [Đổi theo AI]  [Hủy]
   ```

2. **Style guide**: Dropdown [Style](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#45-3524) quét thư mục `styles/` cho file [.json](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/settings.json), lọc theo `pipeline` field ([review](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/chapter_tab.py#373-376) cho Top/List, [narrative](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1489-1533) cho Narrative). Hiện tại có 4 style files:
   - `Review_súng_đạn.json` (review pipeline)
   - `Review_trang_thiết_bị_quân_sự.json` (review pipeline)
   - `Review_bí_ẩn_lịch_sử.json` (review pipeline)
   - `narrative_phân_tích_trận_đánh.json` (narrative pipeline)

3. **Merge mode**: Chỉ khả dụng khi >1 URL + mode Top/List. Pipeline: download & split riêng từng video → gom tất cả chapters → tạo 1 rewrite job (giống [_do_rewrite_merge](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#1673-1709) trong [rewrite_style_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py)).

