## Verification Plan

### Manual Testing
1. **Single URL**: Paste 1 link → Run → Verify 3 output folders (download/chapters/rewrite)
2. **Multi-URL Independent**: Paste 3 links → "Independent" → 3 separate projects
3. **Multi-URL Merge**: Paste 2 links → "Merge" → 1 rewrite job từ merged chapters
4. **Mismatch popup**: Paste link narrative video while mode=Top/List → popup hiện đúng title
5. **Stop/Error**: Paste invalid URL → verify error handled, app không crash
